sinopsis_idioma_original:
About a trace of love. Sometimes I masturbate to reveal an passed relationship;
Form the shape in illusion to fulfill the heart taken by the vanish of odor;
Catch the shadow of sparkling memory in lusciousness to keep the unaccomplished promise;
Ruminate all those shedding and remain, my body becomes shinny and smooth,
reflect the ‘me’ that Liu have never seen.
